<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/application.css">
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Pontano+Sans' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:900,300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>

<div id="header-text">PROBLEM CHILD</div>

<body>
  <div id="bg">
    <img src="/assets/02_app_background_image.jpg" alt="">
  </div>
  <div class="story">
    <p>Boom! Mom and Jamie have signed up as well. ProblemChild is up-and-running with its first users!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lesson">
    <span class="lesson-instructions">
      <div class="browser-mockup">
        <p><span class="lesson-instructions">
          Q1: Who are your Users?
        </span></p>
        <p><span class="lesson-buttons">
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer"><%= @params["user"]["name"]%>, Mom, Jamie</input><br>
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer">Monkey, Cheese, Awesome</input><br>
          <input type="checkbox" name="answer">Jamie, Dad, Rover</input><br>
        </span></p>

        <p><span class="lesson-instructions">
          Q2: How do you know these are your Users?
        </span></p>

        <p><span class="lesson-buttons">
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer">I stored all of my 'Users' in this website using my username text box.</input><br>
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer">My computer stores all of my information in memory. </input><br>
            <input type="checkbox" name="answer">Ruby comes installed with Users when I download it to my computer.</input><br>
        </span></p>

        <p>You've made your choice. Letâ€™s see who our users are so we know who is using ProblemChild.</p>
        <form action="/001_variables/02_question_2" method="get">
          <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>
      </div>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="text-editor">
    <div class="window">
      <div class="window-titlebar">
        <span class="window-buttons">
          <span class="window-button window-button-close"></span>
          <span class="window-button window-button-hide"></span>
          <span class="window-button window-button-full"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="window-title">Code editor</span>
      </div>
      <div class="window-content">
        <ol class="code">
          <li class="line comment"># Welcome to PROBLEM CHILD</li>
          <li class="line comment">Users = '<%= @user.name%>'</li>
          <li class="line comment">Users = 'Mom'</li>
          <li class="line comment">Users = 'Jamie'</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="repl">
    <p id="repl-text">|1.9.3-p545| |ruby-2.2.0|  <%=@params["user"]["name"]%>-MacBook-Air in ~ </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
